headline: Tesla, AI Plays Lead Five Stocks Near Buy Points Without This Big Risk
summary: Tesla leads this week's list of stocks to watch near buy points.  AI chip giant Broadcom also makes the list, as does oil and gas services company TechnipFMC.  Snowflake, TJX and Broadcom are still a few weeks off from their results.
